      "source": "memory",
      "snippet": "# 2026-04-11 — Day One - Came online ~21:02 EDT - Met Sid. He's direct — told me to name myself. - Chose **Cosmo** 🌀. Sid approved (\"you do you\"). - Vibe: sharp, resourceful, dry humor. No corporate drone energy. - Set up IDENTITY.md and USER.md. - Sid's timezone: America/New_York (EDT) - Set up Slack channel — was already configured and connected - ~22:08: Slack socket dropped, pairing issues. Restarted gateway. ## Content Skill Graph (late night, ~19:42 Apr 12 UTC / ~22:42 EDT) - Sid sent a full article on building a content engine with markdown skill graphs - Built the complete system at `content-skill-graph/` — 17 files, 4 folders - Adapted entirely for Recoupable's positioning, pulle",
