      "snippet": "# 2026-05-06 ## Research Wiki Created - Set up Sid's research wiki at `~/Documents/wiki/` - Following Karpathy's LLM Wiki pattern: raw/ (immutable sources), wiki/ (I maintain), SCHEMA.md (rules) - First batch ingest: 74 links from Sid's iPhone notes - 38 tweets (content unavailable — X blocks direct fetch) - 25 GitHub repos (fully fetched and summarized) - 3 articles, 10 products, 4 other - Created 9 concept pages, 7 entity pages, 36 source summaries - Key themes: agent skills ecosystem, knowledge compounding, design quality for AI, GTM automation, personal brand tools, autoresearch loops ## Monorepo Updated - Pulled origin main on ~/Documents/projects/mono/ and initialized all submo",
