      "source": "memory",
      "snippet": "- Pulse ran successfully: 38 ideas discovered from YouTube + RSS - Dashboard verified working: Review, Backlog, Pipeline, Performance tabs all functional - Voice profile built from strategy repo tweets ### Morning Workflow for Sid 1. `npm run dashboard` (or I can do it via heartbeat) 2. Open http://localhost:3456 → Review tab 3. Swipe ideas: ← skip, → keep, ↑ star (keyboard shortcuts) 4. I run `npm run generate` to create drafts 5. Pipeline tab → review/edit/approve drafts 6. I run `npm run approve` to publish via Postiz ### v2 Update (2:14 AM) Sid asked for slides/carousels + general AI trends. Added: - *Carousel renderer:* HTML templates → Playwright screenshots. 1080×1350 LinkedIn forma",
