      "snippet": "- Page: `app/pricing/page.tsx` — 3-tier pricing grid, FAQ accordion, bottom CTA - Committed to marketing submodule (commit f21871a) ### Why This Matters - No dedicated pricing page existed — homepage had a brief pricing section but no SEO-targetable page - Pricing pages are the #1 conversion page for SaaS — prospects actively seeking them are high-intent - Now targetable for \"AI music marketing pricing\" SEO queries - Can be linked from every blog post, social post, and email - FAQ section handles 8 common objections (credits, safety, integrations, ChatGPT comparison) ### What's Still Needed - `pnpm install` to restore node_modules (couldn't build-verify without it) - Push to remote / deplo",
