      "source": "memory",
      "snippet": "# 2026-05-07 ## The $100k/mo Mandate Sid set the north star: $100k/month revenue as fast as possible. All streams count — Recoupable, consulting, thought leadership, digital goods, side-SaaS, music catalog. Every nightly session should build something that moves toward this goal. ### Current State (what I gathered) - **Recoupable**: AI agents for the music industry. Product at chat.recoupable.com. Submodules: chat, api, tasks, docs, marketing, admin, cli, skills, open-agents - **Sid's audience**: ~25k X followers, ~2.6k LinkedIn followers, ~1.9k LinkedIn connections - **LinkedIn profile**: Strong narrative — interned for Lil Wayne, produced for Beyoncé/Nicki Minaj, 10+ platinum, Grammy win",
