      "snippet": "- Key findings: - Image posts avg 22.7 engagement vs text-only 8.9 (2.5x) - Sweet spot: 50-150 words (avg 23.3 engagement) - Top hook patterns: personal story (35%), contrarian (30%), specific data (15%) - Zero carousels posted — blue ocean to test - Bottom posts share: vague hooks, listicle/link dumps, engagement bait - Winning formula: specific personal experience + visual + 50-150 words + tension hook ### 4. Content Pipeline — Strategic Roadmap Sid outlined 5 priorities: 1. LinkedIn baseline + flywheel (✅ started — baseline pulled, DB table created) 2. Better discovery (redesign pulse.js around AI Twitter → LinkedIn translation, non-obvious sources, quick triage in Slack) 3.",
