      "endLine": 115,
      "source": "memory",
      "snippet": "4. Slide template iteration (multiple templates, per-platform sizing, A/B testing) 5. Multi-format engine (slides → x articles → blog → newsletter → email — future) ### 5. #cosmo-content Workflow - Channel is now the content dashboard - Flow: I present copy + slides → Sid approves/revises → publish - One post at a time - No separate approval steps — full package in one message ## Decisions - Light mode slides (sky gradient) are the brand direction for editorial content - Skill architecture: top-level process + template variants - LinkedIn baseline informs everything: writing, discovery, hooks - Carousels are the highest-leverage format to test next (images perform 2.5x, carousels untested)",
