      "source": "memory",
      "snippet": "1. `approve.js` — `uploadMedia()` now only trusts local slide PNGs in `data/media/slides/draft-{id}/` or local file paths (JSON array) in `media_urls`. Pre-uploaded Postiz URLs (http) are rejected with a warning. 2. `generate.js` — Added safety clear: any non-carousel draft gets `media_urls = NULL` after insert, preventing stale data. 3. `slack-bridge.js` — `watchReactions` clears `media_urls` on non-carousel drafts before marking approved, as a final guardrail. 4. Cleared stale `media_urls` from draft #19 in DB. 5. Archived old test slide directories (`post-001`, `post-001-v2`, `post-001-v3`, `draft-test`) to `_archive/` so they can't be accidentally reused. **Audit result:** All published",
