      "snippet": "5. Archived old test slide directories (`post-001`, `post-001-v2`, `post-001-v3`, `draft-test`) to `_archive/` so they can't be accidentally reused. **Audit result:** All published drafts confirmed clean. No other drafts have mismatched media. Remaining `ready` drafts (22-25) have no media attached. ## Content Engine Pipeline Overhaul (10:38 AM - 11:48 AM) Sid asked to wipe everything and rebuild the pipeline step by step. Here's what we did: ### Wiped - All 20 drafts deleted - All 120 ideas deleted - DB completely clean ### Pipeline Steps Documented 1. Discovery (pulse.js) → automated 2. Triage (post-triage) → Sid picks topics 👍/👎 3. Generate (generate.js) → automated writer/humanize",
