      "snippet": "- **LinkedIn shareability.** Sid can post \"I built a calculator that shows how much your label spends on marketing vs AI agents. Plug in your numbers:\" → link. This is the kind of content that gets saved and shared. - **Self-qualifying.** Anyone who uses the calculator and sees $50k+ annual savings is a warm advisory lead. The CTA is right there. - **SEO.** \"Music marketing ROI calculator\" is a zero-competition keyword. First to rank = first to capture high-intent search traffic. - **Content engine integration.** Every blog post and playbook chapter can now CTA to /calculator instead of just /pricing. It's a softer, more engaging entry point. ### What's Still Needed - Push to remote + deplo",
